<p><a name="Further_reading" id="Further_reading"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Information_security&amp;action=edit&amp;section=30" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Anderson, K., "<a href="http://www.scmagazineus.com/IT-security-professionals-must-evolve-for-changing-market/article/33990/" class="external text" title="http://www.scmagazineus.com/IT-security-professionals-must-evolve-for-changing-market/article/33990/" rel="nofollow">IT Security Professionals Must Evolve for Changing Market</a>", SC Magazine, <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2006-10-12"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="10-12"><a href="/wiki/October_12" title="October 12">October 12</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2006" title="2006">2006</a></span>.</li>
<li>Aceituno, V., "<a href="http://www.issa.org/Library/Journals/2005/September/Aceituno%20Canal%20-%20On%20Information%20Security%20Paradigms.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.issa.org/Library/Journals/2005/September/Aceituno%20Canal%20-%20On%20Information%20Security%20Paradigms.pdf" rel="nofollow">On Information Security Paradigms</a>",ISSA Journal, September, 2005.</li>
<li>Dhillon, G., "Principles of Information Systems Security: text and cases", John Wiley &amp; Sons, 2007.</li>
<li>Lambo, T."<a href="https://www.issa.org/Library/Journals/2006/November/Lambo-ISO-IEC%2027001-The%20future%20of%20infosec%20certification.pdf" class="external text" title="https://www.issa.org/Library/Journals/2006/November/Lambo-ISO-IEC%2027001-The%20future%20of%20infosec%20certification.pdf" rel="nofollow">ISO/IEC 27001: The future of infosec certification</a>",ISSA Journal, November, 2006.</li>
</ul>
